snippet.title: Jawan | Official Hindi Trailer | Shah Rukh Khan | Atlee | Nayanthara | Vijay S | Deepika P | Anirudh
snippet.description:
Brace yourselves as we present to you the action-packed trailer of #Jawan. Directed by Atlee, the film stars Shah Rukh Khan, Vijay Sethupathi, Nayanthara, and Deepika Padukone (in a special appearance). The film is set to release in cinemas on September 7, 2023 - in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu!

Jawan is a high-octane action thriller which outlines the emotional journey of a man who is set to rectify the wrongs in society.

Starring Shah Rukh Khan, Nayanthara, Vijay Sethupathi and Deepika Padukone (in a special appearance)
Directed - Atlee
Produced - Gauri Khan
Co-Produced - Gaurav Verma
Music - Anirudh
Dop - GK Vishnu
Editor - Ruben
Production Designer - T Muthuraj
Script consultant - Shridhar Raghavan
Guest Lyricist - Irshad Kamil
Lyricist - Kumaar
Rap Written & Performed By - Raja Kumari
Screenplay - Atlee & S. Ramanagirivasan
Dialogues - Sumit Arora
Sound Designer - Kunal Rajan
Choreography - Farah Khan, Shobi & Lalitha, Vaibhavi Merchant

snippet.title: MC STΔN -  NUSTA PAISA  (Official Music Video) | 2023
snippet.description:
Jayega kaam ko, toh khayega shaam ko - MC Stan

Stream "Nusta Paisa": https://mcstan.lnk.to/NustaPaisa

Lyrics: 
Nusta paisa 
Phir kya bolti company 
Sabko Psy

Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa
                   
Meku test mat kar, mein marta ghar dar
Ye diss karra gandu, iska vishaych karta 
Teku dikhna pasand hai re bro, mein shaat nai dikhta 
Mala diss karto aai ghalaya, rukh tere pech likhta 

Mein abhi bade bade logo me, uthta baithta 
Aur tu shemde kider toh pan, fukte baithta
Teko score karne paise nai, mein haste chuthta
Meko malum hai re bro, tu meku copy karta

Arrrrrrrrrrrrrrrrr
Tu phele se kele, bhonda dikhta 
Teku phele pan bola tha, tu bhonda likhta 
Fir kya kaaju pista, aeedha gand me ghusta 
Mein sirf gaane likhta, ann sirf notaa ginta

Tu mera fan nai hai bruh, lekin show pe dikhta
Tu like karta lavde photo khudka 
Mein nai marta sutta 
Mein meri maa ki sunnta 
Teku kon nai sunnta
Ann tu kya pan sunnta 

Tu classes k bhar rukh k, madhiya dhoondta 
Mein carti sunnta, ann tu g** sunnta 
Tu dhating karta, ann mein shooting karta
Mein phele ke dost log se, baat nai karta

Tu hai balish buddi, mein shartir ladka 
Tu hate karta meku, aur mein party karta 
1 week me 3 4 bar, shopping karta
Tu ladki log ke number se, message karta

Teku malum meri capacity 
Mein marte chutha matlab 
!! appa !!
Mi haanat soot to 
Pucchi wani tondacha, tu kai pan bolto 
Tumcha aai cha puccha, tumchya gang lach kolto

Arey call uchal ki shattu ji, stanny boltoy
Kiti vela bollo Tula Nadi nako lagu
Ayee D yho aplay la, vadiuu boltoy
Ghalun takal Tula, svata stanny boltoy

Tumlog ye jo karre na, usko planning bolte hai
Logo ko tum bolne do, woh log kya bhi bolte
Mi aai zavto one side, isleye stanny bolte 
Opp la deun taku, ye kai padri 
Ghosta ae

Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Mera paisa mere jaisa 
Iska paisa uska paisa

Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa
Iska paisa uska paisa 

Tadiwala road, tadi peeta mera homie
Phatki nikla mera khas, mera kattar homie 
Phele kaise thi woh, meku milke change hogayi
Meku pasand nai hai drama, aur woh daily roti 

Only fans unki ban gayeli hai, rozi roti
Squat marke tu hogayeli kitni patli
Mere saath poora india, meri hawa hogayi
Mein bhi rehta teri jaga pe, toh jalan hoti

Shhhhhhhhhhhhhh !!!!

Lafde hogaye mere uss din , daru biru pk
Aage jaana chahte log, mein jana chahta peeche 
Ghumayega mein ek ko, sablog hojayege peeche 
Bich me tere Homie ka, gir gayela wicket

Smoke karu teku jaisa pop smoke vishayyy
Focus karu paise pe, aati uss se bitches
Haath chodho sirf, jab bhi opps log dikhe
Pull up karu shitt, jab bhi cops log dikhe

Yede ki ko woh lera tha, maine bola theek haiiiiiiiii
Ayeeeeee!!! 
SADHU KO JADDU? 
Sabko PSY  
Phir kya bolti company 

Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Mera paisa mere jaisa 
Iska paisa uska paisa

Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Nusta Paisa, Nusta Paisa 
Iska paisa uska paisa

Stay Connected ✅ 

Follow Mc Stan:
INSTAGRAM -  https://www.instagram.com/m___c___stan/
HINDI RECORDS - https://www.instagram.com/hindi_records/

snippet.title: Jawan Trailer REVIEW | Deeksha Sharma
snippet.description:
Jawan Trailer Review By Deeksha Sharma. Jawan Shahrukh Khan Movie Trailer has left everyone shocked with Director Atlee presenting the King of Bollywood in a never seen before Mass Avatar! snippet.title: Jawan: Not Ramaiya Vastavaiya | Shah Rukh Khan | Atlee | Anirudh | Nayanthara | Vishal D | Shilpa R
snippet.description:
Get ready to groove like never before as "Not Ramaiya Vastavaiya", the latest dance track from the highly-anticipated Atlee directorial, Jawan, is out now. The film stars Shah Rukh Khan, Vijay Sethupathi, Nayanthara, and Deepika Padukone (in a special appearance) and is set to release in cinemas on September 7, 2023, in Hindi, Tamil, and Telugu!

#NotRamaiyaVastavaiya out now!

♪Full Song Available on♪ 
JioSaavn: https://bit.ly/3srnLI5
Spotify: https://bit.ly/3ssmbG1
Hungama: https://bit.ly/3OW4upT
Apple Music: https://bit.ly/3OYPyau
Amazon Prime Music: https://bit.ly/44vEozG
Wynk: https://bit.ly/3L0roLy
Resso: https://bit.ly/47UA7Zy
YouTube Music: https://bit.ly/3OWNbov

Music Credits:
Language - Hindi
Song Title - Not Ramaiya Vastavaiya 
Album / Movie - Jawan
Composed by Anirudh Ravichander
Lyrics - Kumaar
Vocals - Anirudh Ravichander, Vishal Dadlani & Shilpa Rao
Choreographer - Vaibhavi Merchant 

Composed, Arranged & Programmed by Anirudh Ravichander
Keyboard, Synth & Rhythm Programmed by Anirudh Ravichander
Whistle - Satish Raghunathan
Tabla - MT Aditya
Additional Rhythm Programmed by Shashank Vijay
Additional Keyboard Programmed by Arish-Pradeep PJ

Music Advisor - Ananthakrrishnan
Creative Consultant - Sajith Satya
Music Editor - Harish Ram L H
Recorded at Albuquerque Records, Chennai. Engineered by Srinivasan M, Shivakiran S, Rajesh Kannan, Jishnu Vijayan
YRF Studios, Mumbai, Engineered by Vijay Dayal & Chinmay
Mixed by Vinay Sridhar & Srinivasan M at Albuquerque Records, Chennai
Mastered by Luca Pretolesi at Studio DMI, Las Vegas Assisted by Alistair Pintus 
Music Coordinator - Velavan B

Lyrics:

Dance with me now I can’t break away
Aaj sari fikreiin tu shake away
Shake away
Dil thirakta dance wale groove pe
Nachun mai to step mera vekh ve

Vekh ve
Aaj sare kaam kal pe talke
Tak dhina dhin nache jayein taal pe
Disko jaz blues sare bhoolke
Desi wale geet pe tu jhoolke
Pehle kiya chaiya chaiya re
Ab kar tha tha thaiyya
Ramiya vasta vaiya..!
Antra

Sama mazedar hua houle houle
Thoda nashedar hua
Man ye dole
Aaj koi nachta hua sa jadu
Sar pe swar hua
Dil ye bole
Doobi khushiyon mein
Raat apni jabse suraj dhala
Chodh sharmana aaj nachle pair chakkle zara

Pahle kiya chaiya chaiiya re
Ab kar tata thaiya
Ramiya vasta vaiyaa..!

snippet.description:
Click here to Subscribe to Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah Official Channel: https://www.youtube.com/taarakmehtakaooltahchashmah?sub_confirmation=1 

Watch the full episodes of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSKo8X_EiY0WewaBlNt49g3

Click here to watch NEW Episode videos: https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzSxhJ6UCi6tgujD-FsAy0sw

Click here to watch your favourite videos from Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah: 
https://www.youtube.com/playlist?list=PLPbh-P_C0BzRYOkpGxKL-6QmvYSL_ZuCu

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. snippet.title: सितंबर के शुरुआती दौर में कई राज्यों में भारी बारिश की आशंका | Skymet Weather
snippet.description:
सितंबर के शुरुआती दौर में बंगाल की खाड़ी में एक निम्न दवा का क्षेत्र बन सकता है जो पश्चिम दिशा में आगे बढ़ते हुए उड़ीसा तटीय आंध्र प्रदेश तेलंगाना विदर्भ मराठवाड़ा सहित मध्य प्रदेश और छत्तीसगढ़ में तेज बारिश देगा। यह मध्य प्रदेश पर आते-आते उत्तर पूर्व की तरफ मुड़ेगा तथा फिर उत्तर प्रदेश बिहार और झारखंड में भी भारी बारिश दे सकता है। परंतु इसका प्रभाव पश्चिमी राजस्थान गुजरात और महाराष्ट्र के तटीय भागों में दिखाई नहीं देगा। पंजाब हरियाणा और दिल्ली का मौसम भी शुष्क बना रहने की संभावना है। दक्षिण भारत में मानसून एक बार फिर सक्रिय हो सकता है।

snippet.description:
In the first T20I, England won the toss and elected to bowl first. New Zealand did not have the best outing with the bat as they could only manage to score 139 runs at the end of the 20 overs. England later chased down the target in just 14 overs and won the match strongly by 7 wickets. England go 1 - 0 up in the series with this sizzling victory.

snippet.title: Ghost Hunters | Comedy | Dreamz Unlimited
snippet.description:
The country is witnessing a sudden outbreak of conjunctivitis (Eye Flu), and cases of pink eye are being reported in higher numbers. Conjunctivitis (Eye Flu), or pink eye, is an irritation or inflammation of the conjunctiva, which covers the white part of the eyeball. It can be caused by allergies or bacterial or viral infection: Conjunctivitis (Eye Flu) can be extremely contagious and is spread by contact with eye secretions from someone who is infected.
We must maintain good hygiene which includes washing hands and avoiding touching eyes with bare or unwashed hands. We must also avoid sharing personal belongings like towels, lenses, or glasses. The area where you live should be cleaned properly.

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3864 | 31 Aug 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3864: Galat Dawai Ki Kahani
--------------------------------------------------------
Abdul explains to everyone how he evaded Danger Bhai and called Inspector Panday to save Dr. Hathi. He narrates the story of how he hid Dr. Hathi inside a washing machine box at the clubhouse. Everyone greets him and thanks him for his bravery. Dr. Hathi later explains to Inspector Panday what really transpired with Danger Bhai's brother Chintamani. Inspector Chaalu Panday announces that Dr. Hathi will also be arrested for the investigation. Will Dr. Hathi be pardoned by Danger Bhai?


Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3864, 31 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

Click here to watch the episode of Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah :

snippet.title: NEW! Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah | Ep 3863 | 30 Aug 2023 | Teaser
snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3863: Inspector Panday Stops Danger Bhai
--------------------------------------------------------
Danger Bhai picks Iyer to administer his massive dose, but he runs. Danger Bhai is still stuck inside the home, so the inhabitants of Gokuldham liberate Sodhi and instead beat up his gang. Later, Danger Bhai escapes the locked flat after a long battle, this time targeting Champaklal. Abdul makes an unsuccessful attempt to save Champaklal. Finally, Inspector Chalu Pandey and his team arrive, and Danger Bhai is apprehended. Watch the episode to find out how Chalu Pandey dealt with Danger Bhai.

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3863, 30 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Raksha Bandhan: वृन्दावन बांके बिहारी जी में पहुंची चिट्ठी, पढ़ा तो पता चला खेल! Banke Bihari Mandir
snippet.description:
राधे राधे, वृंदावन धाम की जय, बांके बिहारी लाल की जय । वृंदावन धाम में दूर-दूर से भक्त आते हैं, कोई ठाकुर जी को पिता मानता है तो कोई भाई ,इस रक्षाबंधन के मौके पर बहनों ने बांके बिहारी जी के लिए राखी एवं संदेश भेजें हैं तो कई बहन ठाकुर जी को मंदिर आकर राखी बांध रही है आई सुनते हैं एक बहन का प्रेम ,बिहारी जी के लिए ।

#bankebiharitemple

#krishnabhajan 
#premanand_ji_maharaj 
#vlog 
#braj

Lyrics:
હું બેની મારી નારે ભીંજાવશો આંખડી રે......... આંખડી રે....... આંખડી રે
બેની મારી પારકી.... બેની મારી પારકી રે
યે બેની મારી નારે ભીંજાવશો આંખડી રે....
હરખ આયો વીરા તને બાંધતા રાખડી રે
હે ઓહુ તારા..... ઓહુ તારા.....ઓહું તારા....
કાળજા ના કટકા કરે ચાર ઓહું તારા (૨)
બેની મારી નારે ભીંજાવશો આંખડી રે
હો મને હરખ થયો વીરા તને બાંધતા રાખડી રે

હું તારા વિના વીરા કોણ હતું મારે મારા કારણે યે ભઈલા દુઃખ વેઠયું ભારે 
એ મારી ઉંમર બેની તને લાગી જાય દુઃખનો વાયરો તને કોઈ દાડે ના વાય (૨)
હો વીરા તું તો મારા જીવતરની લાકડી રે.... લાકડી રે..... લાકડી રે

હે બેની તું તો મારા આંગડિયા નું ફૂલ (૨)
બેની મારી નારે ભીંજાવશો આંખડી રે
આહુડા તારા કાળજા ના કટકા કરે ચાર (૨)
બેની મારી નારી ભીજવશો આ ખડી રે
હું મને હરખ આયો વીરા તને બાંધતા રાખડી રે

હું અમે પારેવડે કાલે ઉડી જાશું
તમારો ઋણ ભઈલા ચમ કરી ચૂકવશું
હો માયા લાગેલી તારી કદી ના ભુલાશે
મારું તો ઠીક ઘરની દીવાલો પણ રડશે
હું ભઈલા જેને ભય નથી તેને કાળી રાતડી રે.... રાતડી રે

મારી લાડકી રી બેની તારા વિના કરશું કોને લાડ (૨)
એની મારી નારી ભીંજાવશો આખડી રે
આહુડા તારા કાળજા ના કટકા ચાર (૨)
બેની મારી નારી ભીંજાવશો આંખડી રે
હું આમ હરખ આયો વીરા તને બાંધતા રાખડી રે મારી લાડકી બેની મારી ભીજાવશો આંખડી રે........

We bring to you the best videos from your favorite show Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah. So, get your daily dose of laughter with Jethalal, Taarak Mehta, Daya, Champaklal and their neighbors in Gokuldham Society.

About Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah:
--------------------------------------------------------------------
The show is inspired from the famous humorous column 'Duniya Ne Undha Chasma' written by the eminent Gujarati writer Mr. Tarak Mehta. This story revolves around daily happenings in "Gokuldham Co-operative Society" and covers topical issues which are socially relevant. The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

The show predominantly - revolves around 'Jethalal' (Dilip Joshi) who is an uneducated Gujarati businessman. Your 'Taarak Mehta', is his neighbor. 'Jethalal' finds a friend and philosopher in 'Taarak Mehta' and often goes to him for advice whenever he is in trouble. Jethalaal's family includes his simpleton wife 'Daya Ben' and a mischievous son 'Tapu'. Tapu is a menace and a constant source of trouble to all the members of Gokuldham. They have often warned 'Jethalal' to reform 'Tapu' or else be prepared to leave the premises. Lost hopes of being heard by his son push Jethalal' to call his father 'Champaklal' from the village. This was his great idea of leashing some control over the mischievous Tapu. The opposite happens and the grandfather joins hands with the grandson to make life a roller coaster troublesome ride for Jethalal.

snippet.title: FRUIT JELLY CAKE | Colorful Healthy Fruit Jelly Cake Recipe Making in Village | Agar Agar Jelly
snippet.description:
Today, in our village, we make colorful fruit jelly using marine algae. We use healthy fruits such as Kiwi, Muskmelon Fruit, Grapes, Green, Grapes, Pomegranate, Mango, Strawberry, Papaya, White Dragon Fruit, Red Dragon Fruit, and Watermelon.

We cool the mixture overnight and get the colorful jelly cake the following day.

Taste is Delicious!

snippet.title: 2023 Hero Karizma XMR - Special? | First Look
snippet.description: The all-new 2023 Hero Karizma XMR is finally here with a new frame, an all-new liquid cooled engine and several new features. Priced at Rs 1.73 lacs (introductory), the new Karizma is the most powerful motorcycle in its category with 25.5PS peak power and 20.4Nm peak torque. This one is claimed to do 0-60kmph in less than six seconds. For the first time, a Karizma has received a full-LED setup, liquid-cooled engine, slip and assist clutch and turn by turn navigation among other new features. Our first ride review will be up on 31st August. Stay tuned.

snippet.title: 2 सितंबर से मानसून कई राज्यों में सक्रिय हरियाणा, दिल्ली, राजस्थान, गुजरात, पश्चिम  एमपी सूखे रहेंगे
snippet.description:
मानसून अब बहुत ही कमजोर हो गया है। एल नीनो का प्रभाव अगस्त के शुरुआती दिनों से ही दिखने लगा था और अब ऐसा लग रहा है कि सितंबर के आखिर तक अलादीन का प्रभाव जारी रहेगा। लेकिन 2 सितंबर से उड़ीसा छत्तीसगढ़ विदर्भ झारखंड और पूर्वी मध्य प्रदेश में बारिश की गतिविधियां बढ़ेगी जो धीरे-धीरे उत्तर प्रदेश और बिहार की तरफ जाएगी। पंजाब के साथ पहाड़ों पर भी हल्की से मध्यम बारिश हो सकती है। दक्षिणी प्रायद्वीप में भी बारिश की गतिविधियों में कुछ वृद्धि हो सकती है। हरियाणा दिल्ली पश्चिमी उत्तर प्रदेश पश्चिम मध्य प्रदेश गुजरात और राजस्थान का मौसम सूखा ही बना रहेगा।

snippet.title: Behna Ne Bhai Ki Kalai Se (बहना ने भाई की कलाई से) With Lyrics | 2023 Raksha Bandhan Superhit  Song
snippet.description:
Song : Resham Ki Dori
Singer: Asha Bhosle, Kishore Kumar, Manna Dey, Mohammed Rafi, Suman Kalyanpur
Lyricist: Hasrat Jaipuri, Indeevar, Neeraj
Music Director: Shankarsinh Raghuwanshi, Jaikishan Dayabhai Pankal
Film Producer: T C Dewan
-------
Lyrics:
behna ne bhai ki kalai se
behna ne bhai ki kalai se pyar bandha hai
pyar ke do taar se sansar bandha hai
resham ki dori se resham ki dori se
resham ki dori se sansar bandha hai
behna ne bhai ki kalai se
behna ne bhai ki kalai se pyar bandha hai
pyar ke do taar se sansar bandha hai
resham ki dori se resham ki dori se
resham ki dori se sansar bandha hai

sundarta me jo kanhaiya hai
mamta me yashodha maiya hai
wo aur nahi dooja koi
wo to mera raja bhaiya hai
behna ne bhai ki kalai se pyar bandha hai
pyar ke do taar se sansar bandha hai
resham ki dori se resham ki dori se
resham ki dori se sansar bandha hai

mera phool hai tu talwar hai tu
meri laaj ka pehredaar hai tu
main akeli kaha is duniya me
mera saara sandar hai tu
behna ne bhai ki kalai se pyar bandha hai
pyar ke do taar se sansar bandha hai
resham ki dori se resham ki dori se
resham ki dori se sansar bandha hai

hume door bhale kismat kar de
apne man se na juda karna
saawan ke paawan din bhaiya
behna ko yaad kiya karna
behna ne bhai ki kalai se pyar bandha hai
pyar ke do taar se sansar bandha hai
resham ki dori se resham ki dori se
resham ki dori se sansar bandha hai
------

snippet.description:
सरिताज किचनची सर्व उत्पादने शुद्ध, पारंपरिक आणि केमिकल विरहित आहेत.

मऊ रसरशीत नारळी भात | नारळीपौर्णिमा स्पेशल पारंपरिक पद्धतीने, मोकळा मऊ नारळीभात Narali Bhat Recipe

नारळी भात | नारळी भात रेसिपी | ओल्या नारळाचा भात | नारळी पौर्णिमा स्पेशल भात | चवदार नारळी भात  | नारळी भात सरिता | गोड नारळी भात | नारळाच्या रेसिपीस | Narali Bhat | Narali Bhat Recipe | Olya Naralacha Bhat | Narali Pournima Special Rice | Tasty Coconut Rice | Narali Bhat Sarita | God Narali Bhat | Coconut Recipes | Marathi Recipes Special | Saritas Kitchen Marathi |   
 
साहित्य | Ingredients - 

भातासाठी 
• तांदूळ - १ कप | Rice – 1 cup
• तूप - २ चमचे | Ghee – 2 tsp
• लवंग - ३ ते ४ | Cloves 
• दालचिनी - १ इंच |Cinnamon – 1 inch
• हिरवी वेलची - २ ते ३ | Cardmom – 2 to 3  
• गरम पाणी - २ कप | Hot water – 2 cup 
• मीठ - चवीप्रमाणे | Salt – As per taste 
• लिंबू रस - १ चमचा | Lemon Juice – 1 tsp 
• नारळ - गुळ शिजवण्यासाठी | Coconut and Jaggery for cooking 
• तूप - २ चमचे |Ghee – 2 tsp
• गुळ - ३/४ कप | Jaggery – ¾ cup
• नारळ - १ कप | Coconut – 1 cup
• काजू बदामचे काप | Chopped Cashewnuts and Almonds 
• पिस्ते | Pistachios

Coconut Rice Recipe – 

• Soak rice for half an hour. 
• In a kadhai add ghee, cloves, cinnamon and rice and saute.
• Add water, lemon juice and salt as per taste. Let them boil.
• After boiling on high heat let water to reduce.
• Some water left then cook this on low heat. 
• After cooked allow the vapor to go out and do not cover. 
• In another pan, add ghee and let jaggery melts and saute.  
• Then add grated coconut and saute this for 2 to 3 minutes.
• In that ready rice add this mixture and saute with hands slowly.
• Let cover and cook on low heat for the 2 minutes.
• In the last add dryfruits.
• Traditional and sweet rice is now ready to eat.
 

Other Recipes – 

फक्त 10 मिनिटात मऊसूत नारळाची बर्फी | Naralachi Barfi Recipe Ft. Masala Kitchen | Saritaskitchen https://youtu.be/ic_RzcFSv2w

"रक्षाबंधन स्पेशल" मऊ लुसलुशीत नेहमीपेक्षा वेगळी सुंदर सुबक ओल्या नारळाची बर्फी। Rakhi Special Barfi https://youtu.be/Fw8GSiSUPxQ

ओल्या नारळाची वडी | महिनाभर टिकणाऱ्या पांढऱ्याशुभ्र मऊ खोबऱ्याच्या वड्या Narlachi Vadi RecipeMarathi https://youtu.be/0FLGonyZZoY

गूळ घालून वेगळ्या चवीच्या मऊसुद ओल्या नारळाची वडी / बर्फी | Coconut Barfi Recipe | Sarita's Kitchen https://youtu.be/LOU463PNSRI

या 6 टिप्स वापरा आणि पाकातील खुसखुशीत रवा नारळ लाडू बनवा / ऑर्डर साठी 1 किलो प्रमाण। दिवाळी फराळ - 1
https://youtu.be/UicyXhSuPNk

नारळाचे लाडू । परफेक्ट, खुसखुशीत वेगळ्या चवीचे नारळाच्या पिठाचे लाडू। Coconut Laddu Sarita's kitchen https://youtu.be/XLuLtFvm6SM

दीड तासात, राखीपौर्णिमा स्पेशल थाळी | व्हेज हांडी, दही आलू आणि बरंच काही Rakshabandhan Special Thali https://youtu.be/OCF3CW8Z3xM

snippet.description:

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 35 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream - 29th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 35 - [Eng Sub] - Neelam Muneer - Imran Abbas - Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream - 29th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

Ehraam-e-Junoon Digitally Presented by Sandal Beauty Cream

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

snippet.description:
Click here to subscribe to SAB: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC6-F5tO8uklgE9Zy8IvbdFw?sub_confirmation=1

Episode 3862: Gokuldham Vs. Danger Bhai
--------------------------------------------------------
Danger Bhai chooses Iyer to give the massive injection, but Iyer manages to escape. Danger Bhai and his associates are safely locked inside the house by Iyer. Everyone at Gokuldham applauds Iyer's activities. The whole Gokuldham society beats the surviving gang member and catches him in the tire. They also arm themselves in order to continue fighting the gang. Bhide receives his utensils, while Taarak receives his home items. Will the people of Gokuldham be able to defeat this fearsome gang?

Show Name – Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah
Star Cast –  Dilip Joshi, Disha Vakani, Amit Bhatt, Nitish Bhaluni
Episodes No - 3862, 29 Aug 2023
Produced By - Asit Kumar Modi

#TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah #तारकमेहताकाउल्टाचश्मा #sab #Latest #New #TaarakMehtaKaOoltahChashmah2023 #tmkocfunnyepisodes #hindicomedy #comedyvideo #15yearsoftmkoc  

About the show: 
----------------------------------------------------------------------
Taarak Mehta Ka Ooltah Chashmah is a SAB Comedy Show inspired by the famous humorous column, Duniya Ne Undha Chashmah written by the eminent Gujarati writer, Mr. Tarak Mehta. This show revolves around the Gada family which consists of businessman, Jethalal Champaklal Gada, Jethalal's wife, Daya & their naughty son, Tipendra Gada living in Gokuldham Co-operative Society, and covers topical issues that are socially relevant. This hilarious show will surely tickle your funny bone.

snippet.title: Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 36 Teaser - 29th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO
snippet.description:
Thanks for watching Har Pal Geo. Please click here https://bit.ly/3rCBCYN to Subscribe and hit the bell icon to enjoy Top Pakistani Dramas and satisfy all your entertainment needs. Do you know Har Pal Geo is now available in the US? Share the News. Spread the word.

Ehraam-e-Junoon Episode 36 Teaser - 29th August 2023 - HAR PAL GEO

"Ehraam-e-Junoon" follows the story of a young and immensely beautiful girl named Shanzay, who is filled with pride and stubbornness due to her upper-class upbringing. Shanzay believes that money can buy everything, including happiness. 

Despite her high standards, Shanzay is yet to find a man who can impress her until she meets Shayan at an event. Shayan is a handsome young man from a middle-class family, who takes up a job as a pizza delivery boy to make ends meet. Shanzay who is immediately drawn to Shayan wants to provide him with a better lifestyle however, Shayan keeps his distance and refuses to accept any of Shanzay’s advances.

As the story unfolds, Shanzay and Shayan's paths cross again and again, and Shanzay begins to question her beliefs about love and money. Will Shayan be the one to break through Shanzay's walls of pride and stubbornness, or will she continue to chase after superficial things?

The drama serial "Ehraam-e-Junoon" promises to take viewers on a rollercoaster ride of emotions as it explores the themes of love, pride, and class differences.

Writer: Jahanzeb Qamar
Director: Syed Ramish Rizvi
Producers: Abdullah Kadwani & Asad Qureshi
Production House: 7th Sky Entertainment
